(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 355.6 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 5de01167-b40c-4b8a-91ed-b1ff2091df81))
(text "EC enumerates to the x86 host as a plain USB device over Mu USB2_P3; firmware exposes keyboard/power/telemetry." (at 20.32 363.22 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 1690881c-2b95-4ec9-9d06-9403fe2f5489))
(text "Touchscreen USB is separate on Mu USB2_P4; sheet 11 owns the retained Intehill USB-C touch/power path." (at 20.32 370.84 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 43b87bea-d55a-4bb2-bb61-d422be3f2593))
(text "Trackpad uses Mu USB2_P8 as a direct internal USB HID pointing device; EC only owns reset/interrupt/sideband." (at 20.32 378.46 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c8460a3c-bd42-4141-add4-ca17ec51b189))
(text "J51 and J55 are DNP alternate/service harnesses; sheets 10/11 own the real display video paths." (at 20.32 386.08 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 7aa97ecd-bf8e-4e23-bdbd-0157eb1fa24b))
(text "Fan PWM/tach are EC-owned. J52 uses fused 5V, 3.3V tach pull-up, and an open-drain PWM sink." (at 20.32 393.7 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 44617be2-bae5-4a8c-8d7b-5331c38f4873))
(text "Thermal control has separate skin/hinge and Mu heatsink NTCs on ADC-capable EC pins." (at 20.32 401.32 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 3690b5ae-a712-4ad0-aeac-da41166e6ba6))
(text "Cooling default is copper spreader/heatpipe/vapor chamber plus quiet blower; no Peltier/TEC in the base design." (at 20.32 408.94 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 8e5f76ff-13e6-4a52-92a6-76d54d55b57a))
(text "Solid-state AirJet-style modules are a future mechanical option, not the assumed electrical baseline." (at 20.32 416.56 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid f14ed42a-d6dc-4a6c-ba7f-18fafa9575dd))
